values: I have a job with a British photogrpaher in Malibu on Friday. The shoot is for Harper's Bazaar. I am creating the possibility of being a hardworker, being fun and doing a great job!. Just thought I would share that with everyone. I am going to be on time as well!

I just watched the movie "The Secret". I love the ideas in there. The law of attraction is amazing. I believe it. Quantum physics is fascinating. I am making it possible to live my life to its full potential. It makes me want to share the ideas with other people. I realized today that the way I contribute to the world is by sharing what I learn with others. I am good at talking and being persuasive. I want to use it for good and be socially conscious. I love life. I am constantly amazed by the universe. The possibility that I am creating for myself and my life is the possibility of being grateful, compassionate, trusting, loving, generous and authentic.
Must Remember that drinky makes me feel unmotivated the next day. Whew.

I'm so proud of myself for finally taking the time get a Live Journal started! I feel like I have a lot going on and I'm excited to write about it. The possibility that I want to create for myself in my life is the possibility of being committed to writing in my journal at least 5 times a week. I know I will learn a lot about myself by doing this and I'm committed to it. I want to do amazing things with my life and this is just the beginning!
